00:20:34.597 --> 00:20:35.597
'Reema!'

00:20:38.437 --> 00:20:39.757
'Kau harus
memberitahuku satu hal.'

00:20:39.997 --> 00:20:40.757
'Apa itu?'

00:20:40.837 --> 00:20:41.957
'Dimana ibumu?'

00:20:42.037 --> 00:20:43.997
'Aku tidak tahu di mana ibuku berada!'

00:20:46.757 --> 00:20:49.557
"Aku hanya tahu dia
dirawat di suatu rumah sakit."

00:20:49.757 --> 00:20:50.757
